Hyatt Regency Dehradun located at the foothills of the Himalayas features 263 well-appointed rooms, including 24 suites with stunning views of the Malsi forest and mountains. 

The pet-friendly hotel also offers multiple distinctive food & beverage venues - each with alfresco seating option, and the Regency Club, Rooftop Pool, Spa & Salon, Stay Fit Studio and Camp Hyatt. 

The event spaces of the hotel are spread across 3115 sqm (33500 sq ft), including the magnificent Regency Ballroom, Vista Lawns, 3 spacious Studios, Pinnacle Lounge and one boardroom.

Welcome to the Hyatt family!

#WorldOfHyatt #HeartoftheHills
